blueprint.label: factories
blueprint.description:
This is the part with the factories that craft things.
It's linked with the logics part in blue. It will get commands, and give back informations about what is being produced.
It also linked to the logistics part in yellow. It's used to manage the sushi-fluids system. Logistics of component is done directly using the logistics system, so it should be in the same logistic network as the factories too. The fluid pipes should be linked too.
